  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41260</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_099_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Dio&gt;……全部、思い出した？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Dio&gt;...do you remember everything now?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41348</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_099_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ああ、うん……
なにもかも思い出した</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Um, yeah...I don't think there's anything else to remember.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41436</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_099_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ずいぶん、遠くまで来ちゃったんだね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We have come a long way...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41552</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_099_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ノルンはオレらを飛ばす場所に
どうして、この星を選んだんだろ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I wonder...Why did Norn choose to make us live on Aselia?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41632</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_099_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ダオスがいるからじゃないかな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It might be because Dhaos was here, don't you think?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41756</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_099_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>わたしたちのこと許せないダオスがいる、
そしてわたしたちもダオスを……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>A person who would never forgive for our transgressions... After all we also destroyed Dhaos's...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41872</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_099_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……やっぱオレらとダオスは
向き合わなくちゃいけない運命かもな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...So it was part of our destiny to face Dhaos...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41936</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_099_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>運命だって</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Destined, huh?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41996</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_099_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>何だよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42076</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_099_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Dio&gt;らしくない単語使ってる</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I've noticed you're learning to use big words recently, huh?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42148</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_099_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……うん……そうだな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Huh...Yeah that's right...!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
</SceneText>
